# patterns/

## What goes here
- Recurring observations with 3+ occurrences across different dates
- Behavioral, market, or operational trends worth tracking

## What does NOT go here
- Single observations (→ `insights/`)
- Actionable decisions based on a pattern (→ `decisions/`)

## Primary Home Test
File here if the observation has appeared 3 or more times.

## Naming Rule
`pattern-name.md` (lowercase, hyphenated). Example: `energy-dip-after-meetings.md`

## Required Sections
- Executive Summary
- Bias Check
- Occurrences (dated list, minimum 3)
- Compiled Truth
- Timeline Evidence
